00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:50,008
    THERE'S SOME EXPLANATION
        FOR WHY YOU HAVE

324
00:16:50,010 --> 00:16:53,244
GIRLS' UNDERWEAR ON YOUR FLOOR.

325
00:16:53,246 --> 00:16:55,046
    - WELL, THERE HAS TO BE,
