00:17:31,718 --> 00:17:33,234
          - BRILLIANT.

339
00:17:33,235 --> 00:17:34,751
  - OH, I WISH I COULD DO THAT
           EVERY DAY.

340
00:17:34,754 --> 00:17:36,821
              AH.

