00:21:09,836 --> 00:21:13,804
- OH, WELL, THAT IS FASCINATING.
        WHAT DID HE SAY?

407
00:21:13,806 --> 00:21:15,706
- WELL, EVIDENTLY HE'S VERY BIG
        IN THE BUSINESS.

408
00:21:15,708 --> 00:21:18,809
           I THINK--
     - WAIT, IS HE REALLY?

