00:21:52,912 --> 00:21:55,579
     - FOLLOW YOUR PASSION,
          YOUR DREAMS.

427
00:21:55,581 --> 00:21:56,747
         GO TO EUROPE.

428
00:21:56,748 --> 00:21:57,914
      FOLLOW YOUR PASSION
        AND YOUR DREAMS.

429
00:21:57,917 --> 00:21:59,650
         GO TO EUROPE.

430
00:21:59,652 --> 00:22:02,620
 - WELL, BUT HERE'S THE THING,
