431
00:22:02,622 --> 00:22:04,622
    HIS DAY JOB HAS BECOME,

432
00:22:04,624 --> 00:22:07,925
           YOU KNOW,
    HIS ABSOLUTE LIVELIHOOD.

433
00:22:07,927 --> 00:22:09,493
           - MM-HMM.

434
00:22:09,495 --> 00:22:11,095
   - AND I THINK THAT'S WHY--
     I WAS TALKING TO HIM,

435
00:22:11,097 --> 00:22:13,531
