    IT'S SO IMPORTANT FOR ME

436
00:22:13,533 --> 00:22:17,735
      TO KEEP THE DAY JOB
   AND, YOU KNOW, THE DREAM,

437
00:22:17,737 --> 00:22:19,970
  THE PASSION, THE MUSIC KIND
  OF SEPARATE FROM EACH OTHER.

